These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cauliflower, grapes, pear, blueberry, broccoli, lime, onion
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, british, indonesian, australian, colombian, egyptian, japanese
 1. the person eating pear is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating blueberry is not the egyptian##6
 3. the canadian is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 4. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 6. the canadian is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 7. the person eating lime is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the british##7
 8. the british is on the left of the japanese##1
 9. the australian is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the indonesian##7
10. the indonesian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
11. the colombian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
13. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating lime##5
14. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
15. the person eating broccoli is the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | pear    | cauliflower    | grapes | lime | blueberry | broccoli    | onion |
| Nationality   | colombian | canadian | indonesian  | egyptian   | australian    | british | japanese |

