.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: grapes, cauliflower, kiwi, mango, potato, asparagus, lettuce
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking, collecting, card-games
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person eating lettuce and the person eating cauliflower##7
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating mango##1
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 6. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
 7. the person eating potato is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person eating cauliflower##7
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
10. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person eating lettuce##6
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person eating mango##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | lettuce  | kiwi | asparagus | mango | grapes     | potato | cauliflower  |
| Hobby   | puzzles | collecting | drawing  | card-games  | woodworking | sudoku      | dancing |

