 3. the fan of gospel is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
 4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 5. the fan of salsa is between the fan of funk and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
 6. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the fan of classical and the fan of dubstep##7
10. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the fan of salsa##6
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
14. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
16. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the fan of funk##6
17. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
18. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
