 8. the person who's sport is caring is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
10. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7
12. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
13. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
