 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 8. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
12. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
13. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the airplane##7
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the boat##1
15. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is basketball##1
